<content>
    
    <section id="id1166740792989">
      <title>The elements</title>
      <para id="id1166741369311">The Group 17 elements have a particular name: the <emphasis effect="italics">halogens</emphasis> meaning <emphasis effect="italics">born of salt</emphasis>. This is due to the formation of salts when they form compounds with a metal. <link target-id="id8830254"/> lists the derivation of the names of the halogens. </para>
