        <para id="id1166736147841">The physical properties of the halogens (<link target-id=" id1166739844915"/>) encompasses gases (F<sub>2</sub> and Cl<sub>2</sub>), a liquid (Br<sub>2</sub>), a non-metallic solid (I<sub>2</sub>), and a metallic metal (At).</para>
