      <section id="id1166735734351">
        <title>Solid state</title>
        <para id="id1856897">Iodine crystallizes in the orthorhombic space group Cmca (<link target-id="id1166741681172"/>). In the solid state, I<sub>2</sub> molecules still contain short I-I bond (2.70 Å).</para>
